# Repository instructions

Read every relevant `docs/**` and `README*` before implementation. Use
repository-local skills under `.agents/skills`; the local package skill routes
to the global canonical package contract. Keep Effects lazy, flat, sequential,
and app-executed. Decode at ingress and encode at outward boundaries. Avoid
generic client callbacks, raw identifiers, primitive semantic config, unchecked
output, runtime type-class branching, pass-through helpers, giant routes, and
service-aware presentation leaves. Run `bun run verification` before handoff.
